  <description><![CDATA[<p>This elegantly appointed hotel offers guests a warm, welcoming atmosphere and high standards of service and cuisine. Signor Mizzaro, the director of the hotel, has welcomed British skiers for many years and is proud of his reputation amongst the hotels in the resort. You will find the atmosphere relaxed and pleasant with a hint of British and Italian culture blended cleverly together. It is situated in the pedestrianised centre of the village, at the foot of the 3-Tre World Cup run and just 1 minute's walk (50m) to the 5 Laghi cable-car.</p>]]></description>
